description: Documents published on 06/24/2020 and from Labor Department

results.title: Rigging Equipment for Material Handling; Extension of the Office of Management and Budget's (OMB) Approval of Information Collection (Paperwork) Requirements
results.abstract: OSHA solicits public comments concerning the proposal to extend the OMB approval of the information collection requirements contained in the Standard on Rigging Equipment for Material Handling. The Standard requires affixing identification tags or markings on rigging equipment, developing and maintaining inspection records, and retaining proof-testing certificates.
